OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FWinds will not be as strong as
OL,6,Fon Wednesday, but scattered, blustery
OL,7,Fshowers continue with some with hail
OL,8,Fand thunder possible. Feeling cool in
OL,9,Fthe brisk winds with temperatures
OL,10,Fremaining below average for mid-May.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FThe wind and showers will
OL,13,Fease overnight, becoming mostly dry by
OL,14,Fmorning. Some clear spells developing
OL,15,Funder lighter winds, allowing for a
OL,16,Fchilly end to the night.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
